sippi_plot_defaults: Sets default options for ploting (such as fontsize)
Call : options==sippi_plot_defaults(options);
% ALWAYS USE DEFULT SETTING (overrules options.axis) overrule=1; % {default overrule=0) options==sippi_plot_defaults(options,overrule);
See also: sippi_plot_posterior, sippi_plot_posterior_2d_marg
